dcterms:title: AgentAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to another Agent.

dcterms:title: AgentIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for an Agent.

dcterms:title: AgentMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing an Agent as content in a Media entity.

dcterms:title: Agent
skos:definition: A person, group, organization or other entity that can act.

dcterms:title: ChronometricAgeAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a chrono:ChronometricAge.

dcterms:title: ChronometricAgeAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a chrono:ChronometricAge.

dcterms:title: ChronometricAgeCitation
skos:definition: A citation of a chrono:ChronometricAge in a bibliographic reference.

dcterms:title: ChronometricAgeMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a chrono:ChronometricAge as content of a Media entity.

dcterms:title: ChronometricAgeProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in the determination of a chrono:ChronometricAge.

dcterms:title: ChronometricAge
skos:definition: An approximation of temporal position (in the sense conveyed by https://www.w3.org/TR/owl-time/#time:TemporalPosition) that is supported by evidence.

dcterms:title: CollectionAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a Collection.

dcterms:title: CollectionAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a Collection.

dcterms:title: CollectionMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a Collection as content in a Media entity.

dcterms:title: Collection
skos:definition: A persistent formal repository in which dwc:MaterialEntities and/or Media are preserved.

dcterms:title: EventAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a dwc:Event.

dcterms:title: EventAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a dwc:Event.

dcterms:title: EventCitation
skos:definition: A citation of a dwc:Event in a bibliographic reference.

dcterms:title: EventIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a dwc:Event.

dcterms:title: EventMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a dwc:Event as content in a Media entity.

dcterms:title: EventProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in a dwc:Event.

dcterms:title: Event
skos:definition: Something that occurs at some location during some time.

dcterms:title: GeneticSequenceAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a GeneticSequence.

dcterms:title: GeneticSequenceAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a GeneticSequence.

dcterms:title: GeneticSequenceCitation
skos:definition: A citation of a GeneticSequence in a bibliographic reference.

dcterms:title: GeneticSequenceMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a GeneticSequence as content in a Media entity.

dcterms:title: GeneticSequenceProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in the determination of a GeneticSequence.

dcterms:title: GeneticSequence
skos:definition: A digital representation of a nucleotide sequence.

dcterms:title: GeologicalContextMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a dwc:GeologicalContext as content of a Media entity.

dcterms:title: GeologicalContext
skos:definition: Geological information, such as stratigraphy, that qualifies a region or place.

dcterms:title: IdentificationAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a dwc:Identification.

dcterms:title: IdentificationTaxon
skos:definition: The components and positions of dwc:scientificNames in dwc:Identifications.

dcterms:title: Identification
skos:definition: A taxonomic determination (i.e., the assignment of dwc:Taxa to dwc:Organisms).

dcterms:title: MaterialAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a dwc:MaterialEntity.

dcterms:title: MaterialAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a dwc:Event.

dcterms:title: MaterialCitation
skos:definition: A citation of a dwc:MaterialEntity in a bibliographic reference.

dcterms:title: MaterialIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a dwc:MaterialEntity.

dcterms:title: MaterialMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a dwc:MaterialEntity as content in a Media entity.

dcterms:title: MaterialProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in the treatment of a dwc:MaterialEntity.

dcterms:title: Material
skos:definition: An entity that can be identified, exist for some period of time, and consist in whole or in part of physical matter while it exists.

dcterms:title: MediaAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a Media entity.

dcterms:title: MediaAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a Media entity.

dcterms:title: MediaIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a Media entity.

dcterms:title: Media
skos:definition: Media (dcmi:Sounds, dcmi:StillImages, dcmi:MovingImages or dcmi:Text) with other entities as content.

dcterms:title: OccurrenceAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a dwc:Occurrence.

dcterms:title: OccurrenceAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a dwc:Occurrence.

dcterms:title: OccurrenceCitation
skos:definition: A citation of a dwc:Occurrence in a bibliographic reference.

dcterms:title: OccurrenceIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a dwc:Occurrence.

dcterms:title: OccurrenceMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a dwc:Occurrence as content in a Media entity.

dcterms:title: OccurrenceProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in the determination of a dwc:Occurrence.

dcterms:title: Occurrence
skos:definition: The state of a dwc:Organism at some location during some time.

dcterms:title: OrganismInteractionAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to an OrgansmInteraction.

dcterms:title: OrganismInteractionAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about an OrganismInteraction.

dcterms:title: OrganismInteractionCitation
skos:definition: A citation of an OrganismInteraction in a bibliographic reference.

dcterms:title: OrganismInteractionMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing an OrganismInteraction as content in a Media entity.

dcterms:title: OrganismInteraction
skos:definition: An interaction between two dwc:Organisms during a dwc:Event.

dcterms:title: PhylogeneticTreeAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a PhylogeneticTree.

dcterms:title: PhylogeneticTreeCitation
skos:definition: A citation of a PhylogeneticTree in a bibliographic reference.

dcterms:title: PhylogeneticTreeIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a PhylogeneticTree.

dcterms:title: PhylogeneticTreeMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a PhylogeneticTree as content in a Media entity.

dcterms:title: PhylogeneticTreeProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in the determination of a PhylogeneticTree.

dcterms:title: PhylogeneticTreeTipAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a PhylogeneticTreeTip.

dcterms:title: PhylogeneticTreeTip
skos:definition: A group of Taxa at the end of a branch of a PhylogeneticTree as determined from relationships between dwc:Organisms.

dcterms:title: PhylogeneticTree
skos:definition: A branching diagram that shows the evolutionary relationships between dwc:Organisms.

dcterms:title: ProtocolCitation
skos:definition: A citation of a Protocol in a bibliographic reference.

dcterms:title: Protocol
skos:definition: A method used during an action.

dcterms:title: Relationship
skos:definition: A specification for a relationship of a subject entity to a related entity.

dcterms:title: SurveyAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a Survey.

dcterms:title: SurveyAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a Survey.

dcterms:title: SurveyCitation
skos:definition: A citation of a Survey in a bibliographic reference.

dcterms:title: SurveyIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a Survey.

dcterms:title: SurveyProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in a Survey.

dcterms:title: SurveyTarget
skos:definition: A specification of a characteristic of dwc:Occurrence that was included or excluded in a Survey.

dcterms:title: Survey
skos:definition: A biotic survey.
